{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"12808","heading":"Second mortgage assistance for first-time homebuyers","label":"12808 Second mortgage assistance for first-time homebuyers","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch130/schII/ptD","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall make available a model program under which units of general local government provide loans (secured by second mortgages) with deferred payment of interest and principal to first-time homebuyers.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Homeownership counseling","label":"b Homeownership counseling","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"counseling before and after purchase of the property;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"assisting first-time homebuyers in identifying the most suitable and affordable properties;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"providing homebuyers with financial management assistance;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"assisting homebuyers in understanding mortgage transactions and home sales contracts; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fb%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"assisting homebuyers with eliminating any credit problems that may prevent the homebuyers from purchasing the property.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Eligibility requirements","label":"c Eligibility requirements","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the homebuyer assisted is a first-time homebuyer;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the property secured by the second mortgage is a single-family residence and is the principal residence of the homebuyer; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the principal obligation of the deferred payment loan secured by a second mortgage does not exceed 30 percent of the acquisition price of the residence to the homebuyer.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Payment terms","label":"d Payment terms","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Period of deferral","label":"1 Period of deferral","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The payment of any principal and interest on a loan under this section shall be deferred for not less than the 5-year period beginning on the date of the acquisition of the residence by the homebuyer.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Interest rate","label":"2 Interest rate","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The interest rate on the unpaid balance of a loan under this section shall be at least 4 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Repayment period","label":"3 Repayment period","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A deferred payment loan secured by a second mortgage shall be repayable over the 15-year period beginning at the end of the deferral period.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Security","label":"e Security","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12808","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs12808%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A deferred payment loan assisted with amount provided under a grant under this section shall be secured by a lien on the property involved, which lien shall be subordinate to the first mortgage on the property.1So in original. Probably should be “amounts”.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
